article.description: — Jaylen Forbes had 20 points as Tulane defeated East Carolina 60-56 on Saturday.
article.headline: Forbes scores 20 and Tulane beats East Carolina 60-56
article.linkText: Forbes scores 20 and Tulane beats East Carolina 60-56
article.story: NEW ORLEANS -- — Jaylen Forbes had 20 points as Tulane defeated East Carolina 60-56 on Saturday. Gabe Watson had 13 points for Tulane (6-2, 1-2 American Athletic Conference). Jordan Walker added 10 points. Kevin Cross had seven rebounds. Brandon Suggs had 14 points and eight rebounds for the Pirates (7-2, 1-2). J.J. Miles added 11 points. Jayden Gardner had seven rebounds. The Green Wave leveled the season series against the Pirates and ended a six-game losing streak versus East Carolina with the win. East Carolina defeated Tulane 68-58 on Dec. 22. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
